                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">British Ambassador</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lenox, Mass.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-07-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 30, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Can you inform me whether United States Government intend to demand extradition
                    of Harry L. Holmes, now held at Montreal for theft?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Durand.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
